text: Russell Dwayne Mark Leverock (born 14 July 1971) is a former Bermudian cricketer. He played 34 One-day internationals and 2 Twenty20 Internationals for Bermuda at the 2007 Cricket World Cup. He is the uncle of cricketer Kamau Leverock. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Bermudian cricketers
